Yugoslavia," the spokesman said.
</P>
<P>
International efforts should be concentrated on rendering "
nondiscriminatory aid to the Yugoslav people to help stop the
grave economic and humanitarian crisis caused by three months of
barbarous bombings (by NATO)," he said. 
