<HEADLINE> CPPCC Vice-Chairman Meets With DPRK Visitors </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, July 13 (Xinhua) -- Zhao Nanqi, a vice-chairman of the
Chinese People's Political Consultative Conference (CPPCC)
National Committee, met here today with Kang Ryen Hak, president
of the Central Committee of the Democratic Front for the
Reunification of the Fatherland (DFRF) of the Democratic People's
Republic of Korea (DPRK), and his party.
</P>
