<HEADLINE> Tehran Stock Exchange Index Closes Down </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
TEHRAN, July 13 (Xinhua) -- The general price index at Tehran
Stock Exchange on Tuesday closed at 1,739.15 points, down 0.68
points from Monday' finish.
</P>
<P>
A total of 2,217,562 shares changed hands in 1,027 turns and
the turnover stood at 10.20 billion rials (about 3.4 million
U.S. dollars).
</P>
<P>
