<HEADLINE> Team Final Results of Asian Juniors Badminton </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
YANGON, July 13 (Xinhua) -- Following are the team events final
results of the Asian Juniors Badminton Championship here on
Tuesday:
</P>
<P>
Girls' team final result:
</P>
<P>
China bt Indonesia 5-0
</P>
<P>
Hu Ting, China, bt Atu Rosalina S, Indonesia, 11-0, 13-10
</P>
<P>
Xie Xingfang, China, bt Mona Santoso, Indonesia, 11-5, 11-8
</P>
<P>
Wei Yan, China, bt Chiung Siang, Indonesia, 11-1, 11-3
</P>
<P>
Xie Xingfang and Zhang Jiewen, China, bt Novita and Enny E,
Indonesia, 15-6, 15-9
