<HEADLINE> Mongolian President Hails Coming Visit by Chinese President </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
ULAN BATOR, July 13 (Xinhua) -- Mongolian President Nachagyn
Bagabandy has said that the forthcoming state visit by Chinese
President Jiang Zemin to Mongolia will be of great significance
for the development of relations between the two countries.
</P>
<P>
