<HEADLINE> Mexican Stocks Down </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
MEXICO CITY, July 12 (Xinhua) -- The Mexican Stock Exchanges on
Monday closed down with the benchmark IPC index dipping by 119.5
points, or 2.03 percent, at 5,769.37 points.
</P>
